<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1187.111101.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Hind tibiae in male of Phaecadophora spp. A P. dactylina sp. nov. (paratype) B P. vascularis sp. nov. (paratype)." ;
